videos.headline: Hurts connects with Hall for early Oklahoma TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts finds Jeremiah Hall, who reaches into the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hurts connects with Hall for early Oklahoma TD) 2019/09/01

videos.headline: Hurts squeezes in for short TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts pushes into the end zone on a play that is reviewed and eventually ruled a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hurts squeezes in for short TD) 2019/09/01

videos.headline: Hurts goes deep to Lamb for 45-yard TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts finds a wide-open CeeDee Lamb for a 45-yard Oklahoma touchdown, giving the Sooners a 21-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hurts goes deep to Lamb for 45-yard TD) 2019/09/01

videos.headline: King finds Porter for 23-yard Houston TD
videos.description: Houston scores its first touchdown of the season when D'Eriq King connects with Kyle Porter for a 23-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (King finds Porter for 23-yard Houston TD) 2019/09/09

videos.headline: Sermon hurdles over defenders
videos.description: Oklahoma's Trey Surmon leaps over two defenders and steps out of bounds.

videos.headline: Hurts executes 5th TD of the day
videos.description: Jalen Hurts runs in and leaps into the end zone for a 3-yard Sooners touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hurts executes 5th TD of the day) 2019/09/01

videos.headline: Hurts excels in Oklahoma debut
videos.description: Jalen Hurts throws three touchdowns and rushes for three more in Oklahoma's win vs. Houston.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Hurts excels in Oklahoma debut) 2019/09/01 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Hurts expresses disappointment in Oklahoma's performance
videos.description: Despite Jalen Hurts' six-touchdown performance in his Oklahoma debut, he says the Sooners made sloppy plays and need to play better football going forward.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Hurts expresses disappointment in Oklahoma's performance) 2019/09/01
